column5: Ann FYI for the Musky guys Mike Lazarus was on Musky Hunter this week. It may run again later in the week. I did not know who he was but after googling him I saw an old thread OFC thread about him.  I gather he is very well respected in the Musky Community.  I don't know anything about Musky fishing but I find Musky Hunter one of the better shows on WFN.
Mike is the Musky god!  Nobody better
